entries.femaleVariant: <mothertongue l="mex" m="Mi jefe" b="" a=" used to work here."/>

Yeahhh... My old man had a heavy hand, too.

You remember where the eddies is?... 'K, 'K. Talk later.
Well, if that's what he wants...
Hold on, I gotta take this.

<mothertongue l="mex" m="la policia" b="You fuckin' antsy? Not enough action with " a="?"/>

<mothertongue l="mex" m="bróder" b="Whatever, " a="..."/>
Just sat on our couch, quiet. No more questions.
Always be askin' me – "Where you goin'? Where them eddies from?"

Uh-huh...
And the wheels themselves? Whatchu think?
